ry: /Data/soh/result/95/202511/.temp_summary_save_dir\n[2025-11-19 20:30:00] Successfully saved to single HDFS file: /Data/soh/result/95/202511/soh_summary_result.csv\nResults saved to HDFS directory: /Data/soh/result/95/202511/soh_summary_result.csv\n[2025-11-19 20:30:00] Main function finished.\n"
